  <brief_title>A Study of Strontium90 Beta Radiation With Lucentis to Treat Age-Related Macular Degeneration</brief_title>
  <acronym>CABERNET</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Prospective, Active Controlled, Study of the Epi-Rad90™ Ophthalmic System for the Treatment of Subfoveal Choroidal Neovascularization Associated With Wet Age-Related Macular Degeneration</official_title>
  <sponsors>
